*.nupkg
*.snupkg
**/[Pp]ackages/*
!**/[Pp]ackages/build/
*.nuget.props
*.nuget.targets

# ASP.NET / Web
wwwroot/dist/
node_modules/
*.pubxml
*.publishproj
PublishScripts/

